Dear Memphis City Councilors,

My name is [NAME] and I am a resident of [NEIGHBORHOOD]. I am asking to redirect money away from the Memphis PD and into the following social services and community needs: 
* Community Development and Job Creation;
* COVID Relief during this crisis and long-term healthcare;
* Education;
* Housing;
* Child Care;
* Parks & Recreation. 

I request that an emergency meeting be called before the fiscal year goes into effect in order to deny the mayorâ€™s proposed budget and reallocate these funds to resources that promote equity and community well-being for Memphis residents. 

Thank you for your time,

